  <h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400">Monorepo Overview</h3>
  <p class="mb-4 text-white/70">
    Single repository containing all services, agents, frontends, and shared libraries.
    ~46 projects in the Dhadgar.sln solution.
  </p>

